{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "靜候駕臨", "storyInfo": "維多利亞的公爵們都因為諾伯特區的異動而開始行動起來，但救援卻似乎並不是各大公爵的目標。與此同時，諾伯特區的慘劇已經開始蔓延。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“已確認，屬於溫德米爾公爵的一艘高速戰艦遭到薩卡茲不明武器襲擊，沒有倖存者。”"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“初步判斷，該武器就是曾短暫出現在倫蒂尼姆上空的結構體。”"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“經過遠距離觀測小隊的前線評估，該武器強大的滯空能力和源石法術發生裝置的效率值得警惕。”"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“根據現有資訊尚無法判斷薩卡茲製造大型武裝空中載具的技術基底，我們正在試圖掌握更多情報。”"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“然而，在證明薩卡茲擁有的技術可以支援量產該種武器之前，建議暫不把此目標列為最高威脅等級，後續的應對行動已經展開。”"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "37_i14", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "37_i14", "xScaleFrom": 1.3, "yScaleFrom": 1.3, "xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "duration": 20.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“還需注意的是，諾伯特區——倫蒂尼姆的老物流區，在一天前脫離了倫蒂尼姆城市主體。”"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“該地塊現獨自停靠在城市與各大公爵構築的倫蒂尼姆外圍陣線之間。”"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我們有理由懷疑，薩卡茲正在試圖把這個地塊改造成一座前進基地，用以策應他們可預見的一系列大型軍事行動。”"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“這裡也很可能會作為那種薩卡茲大型武器的臨時停靠點。”"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“現任倫蒂尼姆城防軍指揮官萊托中校發佈了一份聲明，他表示因‘技術原因’，諾伯特區意外脫離了倫蒂尼姆主城區。”"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“現在上面仍有大量倫蒂尼姆市民，城防軍正在籌備針對市民的‘救援計劃’。”"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“遠距離觀測小隊提供了數張現場拍攝的照片。”"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "false", "channel": "phone"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "37_i02", "screenadapt": "coverall", "x": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "37_i14", "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“目前，我們還沒有展開任何針對該地塊的大型行動。”"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“但情報人員認為，近八小時內，溫德米爾公爵的移動要塞‘加拉瓦鐵盾’的一系列異常人員調動，很可能與諾伯特區的狀況有關。”"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“有數位分析師指出，溫德米爾公爵對該地塊的軍事主張比我們先前預判的更為激進，具體的原因值得更加深入地調查。”"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“其他各公爵對於這次薩卡茲武裝襲擊的態度與後續行動方向皆處在我方持續監視控管中，本例行分析報告的提交周期會縮短。”"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“等待您的下一步指示。”"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“技術原因”。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很不高明，不是嗎？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是很管用，他們很清楚我們......都很愛護自己的名聲。特別是在維多利亞的未來這件事面前。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#2$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們還拋出了個小小的餌......哼，一艘會飛的要塞？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實很讓人心癢，不過，只要諾伯特區還是他們的擋箭牌，事情就會很麻煩......", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這下，就連威靈頓都不敢直接開著他的高速戰艦衝過來，把老物流區用炮彈犁一遍，然後搶走這個新玩具了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他忍不住的。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，威靈頓公爵的行軍速度加快了，我們認為他也已經掌握了飛空艇的情報。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這種天上的大船確實出乎我們的預料，它有改變未來戰爭形態的潛力。但正如情報所說，事情還遠不到失控的程度。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據我們的估算，就算薩卡茲擁有運送物資的秘密管道，他們也不可能有足夠的資源或時間建設多艘飛空艇。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些魔族佬沒有辦法真正發揮出這項技術的價值，但是我們或許可以。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，當然，這東西很重要，就算我不下命令，你們也會為我拿到它的。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們的眼光不應該只放在一項技術上面。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真正讓我頭疼的是......", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們放任那些薩卡茲待在碎片大廈裡已經太久了，再蠢笨的人恐怕都能研究出那些按鈕背後所代表的東西了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿勒黛......我不怪她，她向來不夠堅決，這是她的優點，我准許她保留這項品質。但我們的“劍座”，看來沒辦法按時啟用了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請您放心，支持您的幾位公爵和他們的屬臣仍堅定地站在您這一邊。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應過給予他們和平與安全，我必須做到。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "永遠兌現承諾，這是開斯特家自古以來的信條。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“灰禮帽”已經在處理了。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，他們總能處理好。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，閣下，諾伯特區的市民......", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊托中校說了，他正在籌備“救援計劃”。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不妨相信這位高盧出身的城防軍指揮官吧，我曾與他見過幾面，他是個有意思的人。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲從來沒有公開聲稱過他們“佔領”了倫蒂尼姆，倫蒂尼姆表面上一直在城防軍的治下。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#9$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這位中校居然在城防軍指揮官的位置上順利活了四年，還沒惹出什麼大亂子來......", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#9$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都知道那些魔族的秉性，這夠讓人敬佩的了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許，有關成為一個“拯救者”，他比我們更感興趣。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白您的意思了。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓合適的人恰當地處在合適的立場上，讓有價值的朋友真的成為忠誠的夥伴......總比我們一開始所期望的要難。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老威靈頓知道我想要什麼，我也知道他想要什麼。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我們從未真正談過這些事，但我們當然會互相幫助，也當然會為彼此多準備一把刀子。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可憐啊，溫德米爾和那些萊塔尼亞人打得太久了，她或許要些時間才能回想起維多利亞的規則是什麼。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們確實還沒有弄清楚，溫德米爾公爵為何也會對諾伯特區的事情如此急切。她也想要飛空艇的技術？", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許是她想讓自己手上的籌碼多一些？她知道自己在未來處境會很尷尬。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "機會永遠與欲望相伴相生，同樣甜蜜，同樣善於引人墮入深淵。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的那位堂兄不明白這一點，所以他已經死了二十六年了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道嗎，有時候，我會夢到他。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我實在說不上喜歡他，他是個誇誇其談，自以為是的傢伙......", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還小的時候，他總是在王宮的走廊上跑來跑去，叫喊著那些從書上看來的先王語錄。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且他嚷嚷的，總是最淺顯的那幾句。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“人民的典範”啦，“貴族的楷模”啦......", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他將這些詞句奉為圭臬，而它們甚至不一定真正出自先王之口，很大機率只是皇家檔案員們諂媚的塗抹罷了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他居然信以為真，他為此付出了代價。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我有時候還是會想念他......", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在的那些年裡，我們仍然可以假裝一切都好。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現如今，再遲鈍的人都必須睜開眼睛了。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "睜眼瞧瞧吧，我們的醜陋，我們的渴求，我們的野心——", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭爆發了，它的來臨終於遂了所有人的願。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閣下，這同樣是個您團結起維多利亞的機會。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，團結......", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞被浮塵沾染太久了，您有資格重塑她的榮光。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是屬於維多利亞的戰爭。", "name": "高級軍官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_408_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不，孩子，這唯獨不屬於維多利亞。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“維多利亞”，我們如此熱愛把祖國的名字掛在嘴邊——", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，它只是人們需要道德時用來遮擋膿瘡的破布，人們需要尊嚴時用來盤剝希望的空殼。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#5$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些農民、工人、士兵、貴族......這些相互敵視、相互仇恨的人，他們的集群憑什麼就成了偉大的維多利亞？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#9$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們每個人口中的維多利亞，指的到底又是什麼？花費了半輩子耕耘的田地，以自己的血淚餵養的工廠......", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#9$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擄掠而來的收藏品，鋪著進口地毯的大廳？還是地圖冊上的一片顏色和一行字母，電視機裡的經濟數字和新聞標題？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#9$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抑或是一個構建在每個人想像之上的，戰無不勝的龐大而榮耀的帝國？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#9$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們做好準備，讓我們屏氣凝神......", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "瞧著吧，看看這場戰爭......會把我們帶往何處去。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g3_fogblockadestreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$escape_intro", "key": "$escape_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_177", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......您好，您——", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我猜猜，你也想被掛在圍欄上？", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，這活計沒那麼有意思，我勸你轉過身，然後滾回你該待的地方。", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不！先生，大人，長官！我只是......大家只是希望我來找您談談......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對，不是談談，只是我們有幾個微不足道的小問題，如果您能大發慈悲......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼時候維多利亞人開始覺得我們魔族佬有副好心腸了？", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是想知道，諾伯特區如今的情況是......？", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼好說的。", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許......您瞧，我們還能湊出點值錢的小玩意，您一定聽說過薩爾貢的寶石，我這裡還有一些......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "滾。", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了，您不感興趣？我還收藏了些舊高盧的油畫，都價值連城——好吧！也許，也許，我不該說的，這會要了我的命......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩科塔的守護銃怎麼樣？機緣巧合之下，我家中珍藏了一把......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真有意思......你有薩科塔的守護銃？", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，算不上擁有！只是暫時保管......天哪，那些公證所的天使知道了會扒了我的皮，但如果您喜歡——", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是聽說，您——薩卡茲一向喜歡收藏這些，那麼......", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽好了，我更喜歡收藏那些剛從死人堆裡撈出來的新鮮天使玩意。現在，滾吧。", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲！我們只是想知道發生了什麼，這是個合理的訴求！", "name": "憤怒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這麼多人被拎出了自己的家，被趕到了這麼狹窄的一個街區裡，沒有住處，沒有食物，沒有自由，現在我們只是想要一個解釋！", "name": "憤怒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多房子還不夠你們住的嗎？敲開——或者撬開，隨便你——一戶人家的門，然後滾進去。你還想要什麼？附帶按摩功能的浴缸？", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們不能這麼對待我們，城防軍在哪裡？我認識萊托，我要和他說話！我們沒有違反任何規定！", "name": "憤怒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "60,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "30,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了，先生，小心......", "name": "菲林女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們帶著武器呢！", "name": "菲林女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "posfrom": "30,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "60,0", "posto": "100,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放開我！我不需要小心什麼！告訴你們，薩卡茲，我在這裡住了三十年，這是我的城市！這是我的街區！", "name": "憤怒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你們接管了那些工廠，你們貪圖倫蒂尼姆的財富，那就拿去，分出幾座工廠並不會損害維多利亞的榮光......", "name": "憤怒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我是個有身份的人，就連國王都不能剝奪我的房子！", "name": "憤怒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我，為什麼一夜之間諾伯特區開出了倫蒂尼姆？街區外面的這些牆是什麼意思？！", "name": "憤怒的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_864_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......你這傢伙就這麼不要命嗎？", "name": "菲林女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_864_1#11$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_053", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_unsheathe", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你憑什麼認為......我沒有權力？", "name": "薩卡茲士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，等等，閣下，老爺！他不是這個意思！", "name": "膽怯的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tear", "volume": 0.7, "delay": 0.3}}, {"id"